flowchart LR
    U[Main User] --> HOME[Homepage]
    HOME --> LIST[Browse Resources]
    HOME --> FORM[Create Listing]
    FORM --> STORE[(Data Storage)]
    STORE --> LIST
    LIST --> SEARCH[Search / Filter]
    SEARCH --> DETAIL[Resource Detail]
    DETAIL --> CONTACT[Contact Owner]
    STORE --> DASH[Dashboard / Summary]

    ADMIN[Admin / Manager] --> ADMINP[Admin Panel]
    ADMINP --> STORE
    ADMINP --> STATUS[Update Resource Status]
    STATUS --> STORE
